<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in North Glenmore Park</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
        <p class="par-lg">Established in 1959, North Glenmore Park is an upscale residential neighborhood located in the South West quadrant of Calgary. </p>
        <p class="par-xl">One of the most sought after neighborhood in the area, North Glenmore enjoys a central location in the heart of the city and offers some of the most idyllic views of the Glenmore Reservoir further south.</p>
        </div>
